Jconf is a library that permits to manage the file-based configuration of programs using json files.

build:
-----

 autoreconf -ivf
 ./configure
 make install ( or sudo make install)

C++ Wrapper:
------------

A C++ 11 wrapper of this library is included  (CppWrapper directory).
To build the C++ library that include the wrapper, the following steps are required:

cd CppWrapper
autoreconf -ivf
./configure
make install ( or sudo make install)
